        building web applications for different clients across the globe giving me a complete perspective of product development
        making me an integral professional focused on business understanding. 
      </p>
      <p class="pl-2 text-justify mb-4">
        With hands-on extensive experience in different technologies, frameworks, patterns and tech stacks,
        I'm well suited to understand the details of complex technical solutions, as well as propose, expand and build on top of them.      
      </p>
      <div class="container grid md:grid-cols-3 grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6 mb-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <Badge>Frontend development</Badge>
          <p class="text-xs dark:text-slate-300 text-slate-600 mt-2">
            HTML / Javascript / Typescript / React / Svelte / 
            NextJS / Vue / Wordpress / Shopify / CSS / Tailwind / SCSS / BEM  
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <Badge>Backend development</Badge>
          <p class="text-xs dark:text-slate-300 text-slate-600 mt-2">
            NodeJs / Express / Python / Django / Ruby / Ruby on Rails / PHP / Larabel / Javal 
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <Badge>Mobile development</Badge>
          <p class="text-xs dark:text-slate-300 text-slate-600 mt-2">
            Expo / React native / Apache Cordova
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <Badge>Scripting</Badge>
         <p class="text-xs dark:text-slate-300 text-slate-600 mt-2">
            Bash / Shell / CI/CD (Bitbucket Pipelines / Jenkins / Github Actions)
        </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <Badge>Databases</Badge>
         <p class="text-xs dark:text-slate-300 text-slate-600 mt-2">
            MySQL / PostgreSQL / MongoDB / Firebase / Graphql
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
