            Agilent Methodologies / SCRUM / Team work / Proficient communication
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>  
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl text-start font-bold mb-2">Bio</h2>
      <Card className="mt-6 mb-4">
        <CardHeader>
          <CardTitle className="text-start text-xl">Technical Lead - Zemoga</CardTitle>
          <CardDescription className="text-start"> May 2023 - Current</CardDescription>
        </CardHeader>
        <CardContent className="text-justify">
          <ul>
